replies.body:
> with one or two exceptions

Resolve isn't really necessary. If you kill your opponent first, you don't need resolve at all. {{champion:7}} {{champion:238}} {{champion:91}} {{champion:157}} {{champion:63}} "Trade" is not a thing anymore. Even some supports can easily kill you in one trade in the laning phase {{champion:432}} {{champion:412}} {{champion:63}} {{summoner:14}} 

Bone plating shouldn't be considered an TRUE defensive rune. It's just a gimmick that helps against poke and can save your ass sometimes.

TRUE defensive runes like Conditioning and Overgrowth - that gives HP/Resist. steroids - are pretty bad on most of champions, with some exceptions as well of course {{champion:86}} {{champion:14}}
